sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Free User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>HistoryScreen (AI sheet)
  participant C as «Control»<br/>SummariseProgress
  participant G as «Gateway»<br/>AiGateway → Edge Function
  A->>B: tap AI summary
  B->>C: summarise(range)
  C->>G: invoke summarise-progress
  note right of G: OpenAI (Gemini fallback) -<br/>basic tier = generic prose
  G-->>C: summary / error
  alt summary returned
    C-->>B: text + model tag
    B-->>A: summary, labelled "AI-assisted - not medical advice"
  else AI unavailable
    C-->>B: AsyncError
    B-->>A: friendly error, retry
  end
  note over C: basic plan = BuildPlanSkeleton (rule-based, no AI)
